892
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:15,360
I was super on edge.

893
00:36:15,870 --> 00:36:17,190
So I really want to

894
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:18,760
win this match.

895
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:20,950
Then I can get the chance

896
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:22,470
