897
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,470
How about we team up?

898
00:36:27,470 --> 00:36:27,950
Come on.

899
00:36:28,430 --> 00:36:29,390
Alright, let's do this.

900
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,670
