902
00:36:33,390 --> 00:36:33,760
Allies.

903
00:36:34,950 --> 00:36:35,470
Really?

904
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:36,120
Or not joining?

905
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:36,710
Come on.

906
00:36:37,080 --> 00:36:38,120
Then it's just us three.

907
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:38,520
I'm in.

908
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,280
Okay.

909
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:42,360
So we take on those three first?

910
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,120
Yeah.

911
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:43,910
Alliance.

912
00:36:44,190 --> 00:36:44,910
They've teamed up.

913
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:47,330
Those three again?

914
00:36:47,910 --> 00:36:48,390
Same team.

915
00:36:48,390 --> 00:36:49,470
Because they live together.

916
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,080
