917
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:54,080
Who should we go after first?

918
00:36:54,080 --> 00:36:55,190
They're way too strong.

919
00:36:58,150 --> 00:36:59,360
Jiawei.

920
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,360
It might not be easy.

921
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,150
It might not be easy.

922
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,000
Or Lu?

923
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,590
Don't target the wrong person.

924
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:14,360
We're a team.

925
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,520
Just don't get hurt.

926
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,470
Be careful.

927
00:37:23,940 --> 00:37:25,740
