928
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,470
Pull it off.

929
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:27,840
Pull.

930
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:29,660
Okay.

931
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:30,720
(Lu Yanting got one point)

932
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:32,670
That's fast.

933
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:32,950
What?

934
00:37:32,950 --> 00:37:33,910
That was fast.

935
00:37:35,080 --> 00:37:35,770
How did he do it?

936
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:36,870
Oh,

937
00:37:36,870 --> 00:37:38,230
Jiawei wanted to let him win

938
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,670
