939
00:37:40,190 --> 00:37:41,760
Jiawei didn't wanted to ask anyone out.

940
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:45,470
I didn't feel like dating back then.

941
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:46,870
All I was thinking was

942
00:37:46,870 --> 00:37:47,520
just...

943
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:50,120
