Lu is my buddy.

945
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:54,520
I wanted to give him a shot at a date.

946
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:11,630
Want a date?

947
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:12,630
Protect.

948
00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:14,190
Want a date?

949
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:16,560
Guan?

950
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:17,470
Yan and

951
00:38:17,870 --> 00:38:18,360
Han.

952
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,360
So today,

953
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,230
