954
00:38:23,040 --> 00:38:23,840
Who doesn't?

955
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:28,390
I got him.

956
00:38:28,390 --> 00:38:29,390
Go.

957
00:38:51,150 --> 00:38:52,670
