959
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:56,300
Enda's.

960
00:38:56,300 --> 00:38:57,940
(Huang Jiawei got one point)

961
00:38:59,710 --> 00:39:01,000
I'm going to grab

962
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:01,810
