1006
00:40:39,430 --> 00:40:40,600
I don't do that.

1007
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:41,490
You and me, one-on-one.

1008
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:42,630
Come on.

1009
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:43,080
Okay.

1010
00:40:43,080 --> 00:40:43,900
