What are they doing?

1012
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:48,120
Then we'll...

1013
00:40:48,470 --> 00:40:49,230
Handle him first.

1014
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:50,390
All of you?

1015
00:40:50,390 --> 00:40:51,230
How about I give up?

1016
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,000
He's giving up.

1017
00:40:53,390 --> 00:40:54,800
This isn't fair, right?

1018
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:56,040
One-on-one.

1019
00:40:56,950 --> 00:40:57,520
Don't.

1020
00:40:57,870 --> 00:40:58,560
One-on-one.

1021
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:00,870
