1026
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,630
He gave each person one point.

1027
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:13,560
It's fine.

1028
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,080
I just want to play.

1029
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:16,710
Yeah, have some fun.

1030
00:41:17,430 --> 00:41:19,280
I honestly didn't plan to go on a date.

1031
00:41:19,340 --> 00:41:21,900
(Flags taken: 3, currently in first place,
