1036
00:41:28,220 --> 00:41:29,140
(Prove myself)
No way.

1037
00:41:29,430 --> 00:41:29,940
I can't lose.

1038
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:31,700
(Hates losing)

1039
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,040
(Trying)
Prove myself.

1040
00:41:33,390 --> 00:41:34,950
First take down two or three flags.

1041
00:41:34,950 --> 00:41:35,560
After that...

1042
00:41:35,620 --> 00:41:36,380
(Master. Score: 3)

1043
00:41:36,390 --> 00:41:37,000
I'm afraid of

1044
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,120
