1052
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:53,130
(Scoreboard: Huang Jiawei 3; Lu Tingyan 2;
Xuan Cheng 1)

1053
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:57,260
(Zhao Enda/Wu Guanjie/
Yang Tianyu/Zhang Zizheng: 0)

1054
00:41:58,870 --> 00:42:00,760
