1063
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,150
They already had the advantage.

1064
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:34,840
Yeah.

1065
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,600
Four to three.

1066
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:37,230
One wrong move

1067
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:38,120
