1068
00:42:38,520 --> 00:42:39,320
Nothing we can do.

1069
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,710
Our alliance didn't really work out.

1070
00:42:40,710 --> 00:42:41,670
We only had three men.

1071
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:44,040
We got ganged up on.

1072
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:46,280
We messed up choosing Guan,

1073
00:42:47,080 --> 00:42:48,050
and then got surrounded,

1074
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,120
surrounded,

1075
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,150
and surrounded.

1076
00:42:50,150 --> 00:42:51,000
(Surrounded)

1077
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,560
In the end, Xuan Cheng could only fight

1078
00:42:52,560 --> 00:42:53,470
