1079
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:55,760
Keep going?

1080
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:56,150
Hold on.

1081
00:43:17,740 --> 00:43:20,100
(Wu Guanjie points +1)

1082
00:43:20,120 --> 00:43:20,520
Alright.

1083
00:43:25,630 --> 00:43:27,560
That game was

1084
