1089
00:43:37,840 --> 00:43:38,910
I checked the leftovers.

1090
00:43:38,910 --> 00:43:39,800
They still look fine.

1091
00:43:39,800 --> 00:43:40,470
Still taste good.

1092
00:43:40,470 --> 00:43:41,630
I had a big bowl of rice.

1093
00:43:46,180 --> 00:43:47,330
