1094
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:49,110
(Scoreboard: Huang Jiawei: 3;
Lu Yanting: 2; Xuan Cheng: 1)

1095
00:43:49,120 --> 00:43:50,540
(Wu Guanjie: 1; Yang Tianyu: 1;
Zhao Enda/Zhang Zizheng: 0)

1096
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:51,000
One-on-one.

1097
00:43:53,150 --> 00:43:53,760
Come on!

1098
00:43:55,630 --> 00:43:56,520
