1101
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:17,430
Impressive.

1102
00:44:17,430 --> 00:44:18,320
Nice one, keep pushing.

1103
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:30,430
When only three players were left,

1104
00:44:31,190 --> 00:44:33,320
me, Tianyu, and Guan,

1105
00:44:33,870 --> 00:44:36,320
I had no edge over either of them.

1106
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:38,080
He's got two points.

1107
00:44:38,710 --> 00:44:39,050
Come on.

1108
00:44:39,710 --> 00:44:40,080
Okay.

1109
00:45:00,840 --> 00:45:01,430
Nice.

1110
00:45:02,180 --> 00:45:04,420
(Yang Tianyu lost 1 flag.
Wu Guanjie points +1, total: 2)

1111
00:45:06,870 --> 00:45:07,630
It's Guan.

1112
00:45:08,840 --> 00:45:09,470
Guan again.

1113
00:45:21,520 --> 00:45:22,190
Watch yourself.

1114
00:45:22,190 --> 00:45:23,000
There's a pole.

1115
00:45:33,280 --> 00:45:34,390
So scary.

1116
00:45:43,540 --> 00:45:44,760
(Tianyu out.
Yanting 3 points)

1117
00:45:45,860 --> 00:45:48,020
(Lu Yanting +1 point (Total: 3))

1118
00:45:50,360 --> 00:45:51,320
That was brilliant.

1119
00:46:00,710 --> 00:46:01,190
Let's go.

1120
00:46:03,390 --> 00:46:04,360
Go, Guan!

1121
00:46:06,280 --> 00:46:07,000
Did Guan tell you

1122
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:07,860
