1123
00:46:08,630 --> 00:46:09,280
I have no idea.

1124
00:46:09,280 --> 00:46:10,670
Oh, you didn't meet before the game.

1125
00:46:12,670 --> 00:46:14,150
Let's go!

1126
00:46:14,780 --> 00:46:15,580
(Two players remain)

1127
00:46:15,600 --> 00:46:16,850
(Huang Jiawei/Lu Yanting: 3; Wu Guanjie: 2)
One-on-one.

1128
00:46:16,860 --> 00:46:17,580
(Yang Tianyu: 2; Xuan Cheng: 1;
Zhao Enda/Zhang Zizheng: 0)

1129
00:46:28,470 --> 00:46:29,420
He still have two flags.

1130
00:46:29,800 --> 00:46:30,040
Yeah.

1131
00:46:31,040 --> 00:46:31,600
I'm worried...

1132
00:46:31,600 --> 00:46:32,910
Don't be, I believe in him.

1133
00:46:33,430 --> 00:46:34,190
It's about scores.

1134
00:46:34,980 --> 00:46:38,540
(Wu Guanjie 2 flags, Lu Yanting 1 flag)

1135
00:46:44,800 --> 00:46:45,950
At the very end,

1136
00:46:45,950 --> 00:46:47,800
