1146
00:47:34,150 --> 00:47:34,910
You're too good!

1147
00:47:35,390 --> 00:47:36,120
Super athletic.

1148
00:47:36,600 --> 00:47:37,230
Yeah.

1149
00:47:37,230 --> 00:47:38,120
No one targeted me.

1150
00:47:38,430 --> 00:47:39,660
Yours were impossible to grab.

1151
00:47:40,080 --> 00:47:40,600
Really?

1152
00:47:40,600 --> 00:47:41,120
Yeah.

1153
00:47:41,300 --> 00:47:41,910
