1167
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:11,230
I need a drink.

1168
00:48:18,360 --> 00:48:19,520
Finally, we can go out to eat.

1169
00:48:19,520 --> 00:48:20,360
Yeah.

1170
00:48:20,360 --> 00:48:22,120
I think we should be able to go out.

1171
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:23,470
I'm starving.

1172
00:48:25,710 --> 00:48:26,360
Today's better.

1173
00:48:26,360 --> 00:48:27,560
No one's hurt too badly.

1174
00:48:28,840 --> 00:48:29,470
Not much else.

1175
00:48:30,430 --> 00:48:31,190
The rain is...

1176
00:48:31,910 --> 00:48:33,000
There's no way to avoid it.

1177
00:48:33,840 --> 00:48:34,870
Once again...

1178
00:48:34,870 --> 00:48:36,950
I let a chance like this slip away.

1179
00:48:37,630 --> 00:48:38,910
Honestly,

1180
00:48:38,910 --> 00:48:39,760
it feels pretty rough.

1181
00:48:40,470 --> 00:48:41,430
Next,

1182
00:48:41,430 --> 00:48:44,000
we'll announce the results
of the Flag Tag Battle.

1183
00:48:44,000 --> 00:48:45,800
The top three islanders

1184
00:48:45,800 --> 00:48:47,190
are

1185
00:48:47,190 --> 00:48:48,390
Wu Guanjie,

1186
00:48:48,710 --> 00:48:49,840
Lu Yanting,

1187
00:48:50,320 --> 00:48:51,280
and Huang Jiawei.

1188
00:48:51,710 --> 00:48:53,390
(Huang Jiawei/Wu Guanjie: 3 pts)
Each of you

1189
00:48:53,390 --> 00:48:55,000
(Lu Yanting: 3 pts. Yang Tianyu: 2 pts)
grabbed three flags,

1190
00:48:55,000 --> 00:48:56,230
(Xuan Cheng: 1. Zhao Enda/Zhang Zizheng: 0)
tied for first place.

1191
00:48:57,300 --> 00:48:59,540
(He's proved himself.)

1192
00:49:00,560 --> 00:49:00,910
I...

1193
00:49:01,600 --> 00:49:02,420
don't want to date.

1194
00:49:02,910 --> 00:49:04,430
So yeah, I'm staying.

1195
00:49:04,430 --> 00:49:05,800
Let's move on to the next person.

1196
00:49:06,870 --> 00:49:07,190
Okay.

1197
00:49:08,150 --> 00:49:10,840
Since islander Huang Jiawei
has withdrawn,

1198
00:49:10,840 --> 00:49:13,120
the fourth-ranked islander, Yang Tianyu,

1199
00:49:13,670 --> 00:49:16,000
your date now takes effect.

1200
00:49:17,040 --> 00:49:17,760
That works?

1201
00:49:18,870 --> 00:49:20,390
We three have no choice.

1202
00:49:22,390 --> 00:49:23,390
You three brothers.

1203
00:49:24,230 --> 00:49:24,910
Adorable.

1204
00:49:25,190 --> 00:49:25,910
Let's go.

1205
00:49:26,320 --> 00:49:27,470
If you're not going out,

1206
00:49:27,470 --> 00:49:28,670
I'll bring you food.

1207
00:49:28,950 --> 00:49:29,280
Okay.

1208
00:49:29,280 --> 00:49:29,840
Don't worry.

1209
00:49:29,840 --> 00:49:31,190
Someone brought me food yesterday.

1210
00:49:31,190 --> 00:49:32,290
Today, count on me.

1211
00:49:32,630 --> 00:49:33,560
Perfect.

1212
00:49:33,560 --> 00:49:35,200
Seems like someone always brings me food.

1213
00:49:37,820 --> 00:49:38,780
(Male Room 3)

1214
00:49:38,800 --> 00:49:39,950
How am I supposed to go out?

1215
00:49:41,120 --> 00:49:42,040
Look at what I drew.

1216
00:49:42,040 --> 00:49:43,040
I got Yang

1217
00:49:43,040 --> 00:49:43,900
and Yijia.

1218
00:49:44,420 --> 00:49:47,780
(Date Card: Huang Jiawei.
Chen Yijia. Yang Tinghong)

1219
00:49:48,080 --> 00:49:48,600
Well, well.

1220
00:49:50,120 --> 00:49:51,470
How am I supposed to go with Yang?

1221
00:49:52,280 --> 00:49:53,520
It wouldn't mean much for me.

1222
00:49:53,910 --> 00:49:55,330
I don't even have feelings for them.

1223
00:49:56,390 --> 00:49:56,670
Right?

1224
00:49:57,120 --> 00:49:58,630
Why take up a spot for no reason?

1225
00:49:59,400 --> 00:50:00,460
Let's see which lovely lady

1226
00:50:00,460 --> 00:50:01,630
is going out for a nice meal?

1227
00:50:02,560 --> 00:50:03,760
Remember to bring food back.

1228
00:50:03,760 --> 00:50:04,990
You might be the one going out.

1229
00:50:05,230 --> 00:50:06,120
No one picked me.

1230
00:50:06,430 --> 00:50:07,120
How do you know?

1231
00:50:07,320 --> 00:50:08,320
Seriously, no one.

1232
00:50:08,630 --> 00:50:09,320
You know it?

1233
00:50:09,630 --> 00:50:10,190
Just guessing.

1234
00:50:11,470 --> 00:50:12,250
You little rascal.

1235
00:50:14,840 --> 00:50:15,560
You know what,

1236
00:50:15,870 --> 00:50:17,280
I heard it's two...

1237
00:50:17,630 --> 00:50:18,080
Two what?

1238
00:50:18,430 --> 00:50:19,230
One guy, two girls.

1239
00:50:19,230 --> 00:50:20,470
One guy has to choose two girls.

1240
00:50:21,280 --> 00:50:22,470
One guy with two girls?

1241
00:50:22,470 --> 00:50:23,390
Are they serious?

1242
00:50:24,000 --> 00:50:25,080
That's pretty wild.

1243
00:50:25,600 --> 00:50:25,950
Yeah.

1244
00:50:26,390 --> 00:50:27,720
Not sure if they all eat together

1245
00:50:27,720 --> 00:50:28,430
or separately.

1246
00:50:28,430 --> 00:50:29,600
That's insane.

1247
00:50:29,600 --> 00:50:30,320
Three people?

1248
00:50:30,710 --> 00:50:31,560
I think it's possible.

1249
00:50:31,560 --> 00:50:32,280
This is nuts.

1250
00:50:32,470 --> 00:50:32,800
Yeah.

1251
00:50:32,800 --> 00:50:33,470
Eating together.

1252
00:50:33,470 --> 00:50:33,950
Could be.

1253
00:50:36,910 --> 00:50:37,560
What a drama.

1254
00:50:38,080 --> 00:50:39,760
Don't tell me it's one guy with...

1255
00:50:39,760 --> 00:50:40,800
two girls going on a date.

1256
00:50:41,230 --> 00:50:43,040
I don't think so.

1257
00:50:43,470 --> 00:50:45,150
I still have no idea who I'm dating.

1258
00:50:47,840 --> 00:50:50,120
Let's go. Have a good time. Bye.

1259
00:50:50,140 --> 00:50:53,180
(Heading to dating location)

1260
00:50:58,940 --> 00:51:01,500
(All islanders going on a date
have left the island)

1261
00:51:03,040 --> 00:51:04,630
I'll go see if Han's here.

1262
00:51:05,040 --> 00:51:05,910
Han.

1263
00:51:05,910 --> 00:51:07,150
Please be here.

1264
00:51:07,150 --> 00:51:08,150
Han.

1265
00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:10,710
What if I knock and she's not there?

1266
00:51:11,040 --> 00:51:11,870
My heart would break.

1267
00:51:15,760 --> 00:51:16,710
What if Han is picked?

1268
00:51:17,600 --> 00:51:18,280
I'd lose it.

1269
00:51:21,870 --> 00:51:22,800
Time to eat.

1270
00:51:23,080 --> 00:51:24,390
Your Enda.

1271
00:51:24,390 --> 00:51:25,320
(Yang Tinghong and Zhu Huiyan: no date)

1272
00:51:25,320 --> 00:51:26,330
He's here to pick you up.

1273
00:51:26,560 --> 00:51:27,230
Go with him.

1274
00:51:27,230 --> 00:51:28,100
I'll go on my own.

1275
00:51:28,100 --> 00:51:31,020
(Yang Tinghong & Zhu Huiyan's room.
Liu Jiayi & Wu Yihan's room)

1276
00:51:31,040 --> 00:51:31,800
Is she there?

1277
00:51:32,710 --> 00:51:33,430
Yeah.

1278
00:51:33,430 --> 00:51:34,560
No one is answering the door.

1279
00:51:36,360 --> 00:51:37,360
Both of them are here.

1280
00:51:38,950 --> 00:51:39,950
Both of them?

1281
00:51:39,950 --> 00:51:40,950
Yan's here too?

1282
00:51:44,470 --> 00:51:45,950
Wasn't Guan's first pick Yan?

1283
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:50,000
I think Guan actually picked...

1284
00:51:51,840 --> 00:51:53,000
Han and Yijia.

1285
00:51:55,360 --> 00:51:56,600
He probably chose Yijia first.

1286
00:51:57,800 --> 00:51:58,390
Not sure.

1287
00:51:59,840 --> 00:52:00,670
Hello.

1288
00:52:00,670 --> 00:52:01,360
Is Yan here?

1289
00:52:01,360 --> 00:52:01,910
She's here.

1290
00:52:02,870 --> 00:52:04,040
My Han got asked out.

1291
00:52:04,430 --> 00:52:05,080
By who?

1292
00:52:06,150 --> 00:52:08,080
I guess it must be...

1293
00:52:08,080 --> 00:52:08,870
Tianyu?

1294
00:52:08,870 --> 00:52:10,040
Yeah. Oh, nah.

1295
00:52:10,040 --> 00:52:10,470
Who then?

1296
00:52:10,470 --> 00:52:11,230
Guan.

1297
00:52:11,760 --> 00:52:12,320
Seriously?

1298
00:52:13,800 --> 00:52:14,870
Then it's over.

1299
00:52:15,150 --> 00:52:15,560
Over.

1300
00:52:16,190 --> 00:52:16,630
She's got

1301
00:52:16,630 --> 00:52:17,840
a bit unhappy about it.

1302
00:52:19,520 --> 00:52:20,600
Is Han here?

1303
00:52:20,600 --> 00:52:21,150
No, she's not.

1304
00:52:21,150 --> 00:52:22,000
God darn, bro.

1305
00:52:22,470 --> 00:52:23,560
So who picked her then?

1306
00:52:24,360 --> 00:52:24,870
I think

1307
00:52:24,870 --> 00:52:26,000
it's the second choice.

1308
00:52:26,190 --> 00:52:26,630
Yeah.

1309
00:52:26,630 --> 00:52:27,840
The date just landed on her.

1310
00:52:27,840 --> 00:52:28,190
Exactly.

1311
00:52:28,190 --> 00:52:29,080
It's fine, let's eat.

1312
00:52:30,470 --> 00:52:31,190
Take a guess who?

1313
00:52:31,950 --> 00:52:32,280
No need.

1314
00:52:32,280 --> 00:52:33,040
Guan.

1315
00:52:33,910 --> 00:52:35,150
No.

1316
00:52:35,280 --> 00:52:36,080
Tianyu.

1317
00:52:36,080 --> 00:52:36,670
Could be.

1318
00:52:37,630 --> 00:52:38,910
Why only these people?

1319
00:52:39,390 --> 00:52:40,760
The others all went out on dates.

1320
00:52:42,560 --> 00:52:43,470
They've all left.

1321
00:52:43,470 --> 00:52:44,760
Just the few of us left.

1322
00:52:44,760 --> 00:52:45,360
And Yan.

1323
00:52:45,360 --> 00:52:46,000
Yan.

1324
00:52:46,000 --> 00:52:46,590
She's not here.

1325
00:52:46,590 --> 00:52:47,390
She is.

1326
00:52:47,390 --> 00:52:47,950
In her room.

1327
00:52:47,950 --> 00:52:48,460
Yan's here.

1328
00:52:49,450 --> 00:52:50,600
She doesn't want to come out.

1329
00:52:50,600 --> 00:52:50,840
Yeah.

1330
00:52:50,840 --> 00:52:51,560
She's upset.

1331
00:52:51,560 --> 00:52:52,670
She feels kinda...

1332
00:52:52,670 --> 00:52:53,670
Because she's left out?

1333
00:52:53,670 --> 00:52:54,230
No.

1334
00:52:54,230 --> 00:52:55,590
She doesn't know if she was chosen.

1335
00:52:56,080 --> 00:52:57,120
She still has no idea.

1336
00:52:57,360 --> 00:52:58,390
They've already left.

1337
00:52:58,390 --> 00:53:00,520
Yeah, but she really doesn't know.

1338
00:53:01,000 --> 00:53:01,630
Whatever.

1339
00:53:01,630 --> 00:53:02,300
Never mind.

1340
00:53:02,300 --> 00:53:02,910
Not my concern.

1341
00:53:02,910 --> 00:53:04,080
Let's eat first.

1342
00:53:05,120 --> 00:53:07,000
I was as shocked as you guys.

1343
00:53:08,900 --> 00:53:09,700
Drama.

1344
00:53:10,940 --> 00:53:11,830
Drama.

1345
00:53:12,590 --> 00:53:13,380
But...

1346
00:53:13,830 --> 00:53:14,380
Wait.

1347
00:53:15,310 --> 00:53:16,030
Listen, I think

1348
00:53:16,420 --> 00:53:17,790
you should still invite her to eat.

1349
00:53:18,180 --> 00:53:19,180
I invited.

1350
00:53:19,180 --> 00:53:20,200
She didn't want to come.

1351
00:53:20,200 --> 00:53:21,180
Why don't you invite her?

1352
00:53:21,180 --> 00:53:21,870
I'm not doing it.

1353
00:53:21,870 --> 00:53:22,510
You go call her.

1354
00:53:27,140 --> 00:53:28,660
Chief, this could be a good chance.

1355
00:53:28,660 --> 00:53:29,740
To ease things up a little.

1356
00:53:29,740 --> 00:53:30,870
We all have to eat anyway.

1357
00:53:30,870 --> 00:53:31,510
True.

1358
00:53:31,510 --> 00:53:33,070
It's just asking her for dinner.

1359
00:53:33,070 --> 00:53:33,790
That's fine.

1360
00:53:34,700 --> 00:53:35,270
Exactly.

1361
00:53:35,590 --> 00:53:36,250
Grab an umbrella.

1362
00:53:36,250 --> 00:53:37,650
Don't feel like using one with her.

1363
00:53:38,900 --> 00:53:40,000
That was absolutely amazing.

1364
00:53:40,110 --> 00:53:42,110
Honestly, kind of unbelievable.

1365
00:53:44,310 --> 00:53:45,460
I need a break.

1366
00:53:45,460 --> 00:53:46,550
I'm drained.

1367
00:53:47,790 --> 00:53:49,270
Will I leave (the island) or not?

1368
00:53:49,270 --> 00:53:52,510
Leave, or stay?

1369
00:53:55,980 --> 00:53:56,870
Who?

1370
00:53:56,870 --> 00:53:57,510
Me.

1371
00:53:58,180 --> 00:53:58,940
Who are you?

1372
00:53:59,460 --> 00:54:00,900
Open the door and you'll see.

1373
00:54:01,900 --> 00:54:02,620
Dinner's ready.

1374
00:54:04,750 --> 00:54:05,380
Thank you.

1375
00:54:06,420 --> 00:54:07,110
Am I the only one

1376
00:54:07,110 --> 00:54:08,140
who hasn't have dinner?

1377
00:54:08,140 --> 00:54:09,070
You're here to call me.

1378
00:54:10,140 --> 00:54:11,900
Why are you alone looking down?

1379
00:54:11,900 --> 00:54:12,900
I'm not feeling down.

1380
00:54:12,900 --> 00:54:14,900
You're not?

1381
00:54:14,900 --> 00:54:16,110
It's just the few of us left.

1382
00:54:16,790 --> 00:54:18,460
Everyone else went out on dates?

1383
00:54:18,460 --> 00:54:19,270
Yeah.

1384
00:54:21,270 --> 00:54:22,110
Nice.

1385
00:54:22,900 --> 00:54:23,980
That's pretty wild

1386
00:54:23,980 --> 00:54:24,830
and kinda mysterious.

1387
00:54:24,830 --> 00:54:26,270
For you, that's actually something.

1388
00:54:27,110 --> 00:54:27,780
Dinner time.

1389
00:54:27,780 --> 00:54:28,980
Eat like there's no tomorrow.

1390
00:54:28,980 --> 00:54:29,550
Go ahead.

1391
00:54:29,700 --> 00:54:31,550
Babe, come eat.

1392
00:54:31,550 --> 00:54:32,070
On my way.

1393
00:54:32,070 --> 00:54:32,980
What's for dinner?

1394
00:54:32,980 --> 00:54:35,310
Honestly, this looks pretty good.

1395
00:54:35,310 --> 00:54:35,980
Time to eat.

1396
00:54:36,380 --> 00:54:37,310
Come on, let's eat.

1397
00:54:38,620 --> 00:54:39,790
But who will Tianyu choose?

1398
00:54:39,790 --> 00:54:40,660
He is hard to read.

1399
00:54:42,070 --> 00:54:43,180
It's gotta be Wan.

1400
00:54:43,180 --> 00:54:43,830
He picked Wan.

1401
00:54:44,180 --> 00:54:44,870
Hey.

1402
00:54:44,870 --> 00:54:46,420
Let's check on Wan, just in case.

1403
00:54:46,420 --> 00:54:46,900
Right.

1404
00:54:46,900 --> 00:54:47,750
What if she's there?

1405
00:54:47,750 --> 00:54:48,140
Exactly.

1406
00:54:48,140 --> 00:54:48,460
I'll...

1407
00:54:48,460 --> 00:54:48,900
You?

1408
00:54:48,900 --> 00:54:49,700
I'm on it.

1409
00:54:49,700 --> 00:54:51,350
Wan? No way.

1410
00:54:51,350 --> 00:54:52,220
She must've left.

1411
00:55:16,490 --> 00:55:19,770
(Ding Wanni & Chen Yijia's room)

1412
00:55:30,270 --> 00:55:31,110
Hello.

1413
00:55:34,070 --> 00:55:34,830
Hello.

1414
00:55:34,830 --> 00:55:35,380
Careful.

1415
00:55:36,980 --> 00:55:38,270
Hello.

1416
00:55:38,270 --> 00:55:38,830
Time to eat.

1417
00:55:39,350 --> 00:55:39,870
Okay.

1418
00:55:40,110 --> 00:55:41,310
So, what's the situation now?

1419
00:55:41,310 --> 00:55:43,110
Basically, it's just the few of us left.

1420
00:55:43,110 --> 00:55:44,220
We're kind of like…

1421
00:55:44,220 --> 00:55:45,940
the left-behind group on the island.

1422
00:55:47,870 --> 00:55:48,750
Gotta cheer up.

1423
00:55:49,700 --> 00:55:51,460
Hello.

1424
00:55:51,460 --> 00:55:52,420
Hello there, folks.

1425
00:55:52,700 --> 00:55:54,140
Seriously?

1426
00:55:54,400 --> 00:55:55,350
I told them you're here.

1427
00:55:55,350 --> 00:55:56,590
They didn't believe me.

1428
00:55:56,590 --> 00:55:57,420
I'm here.

1429
00:55:58,460 --> 00:55:58,870
Right.

1430
00:55:58,870 --> 00:56:00,380
So that's basically round-robin dating.

1431
00:56:00,380 --> 00:56:01,180
Three couples.

1432
00:56:02,900 --> 00:56:03,900
Taking turns.

1433
00:56:04,250 --> 00:56:05,370
(Yang Tianyu & Wu Yihan)

1434
00:56:05,380 --> 00:56:05,940
Take a seat.

1435
00:56:06,460 --> 00:56:07,070
Sure.

1436
00:56:07,950 --> 00:56:08,790
Pass me the umbrella.

1437
00:56:08,790 --> 00:56:09,380
Okay.

1438
00:56:11,350 --> 00:56:13,110
Didn't expect Tianyu to pick me.

1439
00:56:13,110 --> 00:56:14,620
But back on the island,

1440
00:56:14,620 --> 00:56:15,900
we barely talked.

1441
00:56:15,900 --> 00:56:16,750
This time,

1442
00:56:16,750 --> 00:56:18,460
it's nice to get a chance to know him.

1443
00:56:18,790 --> 00:56:19,550
Back then,

1444
00:56:19,550 --> 00:56:20,750
you know how we

1445
00:56:20,750 --> 00:56:21,830
actually made our choice?

1446
00:56:21,830 --> 00:56:22,420
No idea.

1447
00:56:22,420 --> 00:56:24,380
It was your lipstick...

1448
00:56:24,870 --> 00:56:25,900
It should be...

1449
00:56:25,900 --> 00:56:26,940
the two person I picked.

1450
00:56:27,460 --> 00:56:27,950
And then we…

1451
00:56:27,950 --> 00:56:29,740
Pick a mark,
and its owner gets to date.

1452
00:56:29,740 --> 00:56:30,110
Right.

1453
00:56:32,370 --> 00:56:37,050
(Four hours earlier)

1454
00:56:37,070 --> 00:56:39,550
In front of you are the lipstick marks of

1455
00:56:39,550 --> 00:56:41,350
the two girls you'd like to date.

1456
00:56:41,350 --> 00:56:44,030
