1745
01:05:55,940 --> 01:05:56,750
Okay.

1746
01:05:58,310 --> 01:05:58,900
How is it?

1747
01:05:58,900 --> 01:05:59,980
The dessert tastes great.

1748
01:06:02,460 --> 01:06:03,420
We made it ourselves.

1749
01:06:03,940 --> 01:06:05,140
It has to be great.

1750
01:06:06,310 --> 01:06:07,750
She's very straightforward.

1751
01:06:07,750 --> 01:06:10,180
I really like that kind of personality.

1752
01:06:10,180 --> 01:06:12,310
We were talking about our careers

1753
01:06:12,310 --> 01:06:14,140
and relationships,

1754
01:06:14,140 --> 01:06:16,980
all sorts of stuff.
We could talk for hours.

1755
01:06:16,980 --> 01:06:19,070
It actually feels pretty nice.

1756
01:06:19,900 --> 01:06:20,750
I'll get the cake.

1757
01:06:21,110 --> 01:06:21,620
Let me.

1758
01:06:22,750 --> 01:06:23,750
You're not gentle enough.

1759
01:06:23,750 --> 01:06:24,540
You might break it.

1760
01:06:25,750 --> 01:06:26,550
It could get ruined.

1761
01:06:27,140 --> 01:06:28,310
I'll kick it out of here.

1762
01:06:31,590 --> 01:06:32,700
Did you take the photo?

1763
01:06:32,700 --> 01:06:33,350
Yeah, I got it.

1764
01:06:33,350 --> 01:06:33,660
Really?

1765
01:06:33,660 --> 01:06:34,270
Not like you.

1766
01:06:36,030 --> 01:06:36,980
Not like me.

1767
01:06:38,140 --> 01:06:39,140
Still holding a grudge?

1768
01:06:41,590 --> 01:06:42,700
Were you happy today?

1769
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:43,750
Super happy.

1770
01:06:46,030 --> 01:06:47,700
Upset that you can't go out with Han?

1771
01:06:47,900 --> 01:06:48,700
Heartbroken.

1772
01:06:50,900 --> 01:06:52,220
She's sad about her Guan.

1773
01:06:53,220 --> 01:06:54,030
Guan.

1774
01:06:54,030 --> 01:06:55,270
I swear I'm not.

1775
01:06:55,270 --> 01:06:56,510
Guan.

1776
01:07:03,140 --> 01:07:04,180
Have a seat.

1777
01:07:04,270 --> 01:07:04,660
Cold?

1778
01:07:05,110 --> 01:07:06,180
A little bit.

1779
01:07:06,180 --> 01:07:07,220
Put on another layer.

1780
01:07:07,220 --> 01:07:07,980
I caught a cold.

1781
01:07:07,980 --> 01:07:08,840
I'll get you some med.

1782
01:07:09,590 --> 01:07:10,980
You even have a medicine box?

1783
01:07:12,140 --> 01:07:13,030
So, are you happy?

1784
01:07:13,030 --> 01:07:13,620
Really happy.

1785
01:07:13,620 --> 01:07:14,790
That's good then.

1786
01:07:14,940 --> 01:07:16,110
I honestly feel like

1787
01:07:16,110 --> 01:07:18,070
sometimes I just can't figure you out

1788
01:07:18,070 --> 01:07:19,270
or what's on your mind.

1789
01:07:19,270 --> 01:07:20,550
I'll be straight with you.

1790
01:07:20,550 --> 01:07:21,460
I've always thought

1791
01:07:21,460 --> 01:07:22,380
you...

1792
01:07:22,380 --> 01:07:23,220
are pretty great.

1793
01:07:23,530 --> 01:07:40,490
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1794
01:07:40,490 --> 01:07:42,730
(Preview)

1795
01:07:42,750 --> 01:07:43,790
Never thought it'd be you.

1796
01:07:44,140 --> 01:07:45,310
Why'd you pick me?

1797
01:07:45,750 --> 01:07:46,790
That was surprising.

1798
01:07:46,790 --> 01:07:48,220
I mean, I totally guessed wrong.

1799
01:07:48,220 --> 01:07:48,900
But,

1800
01:07:48,900 --> 01:07:50,590
getting to know others isn't bad.

1801
01:07:51,350 --> 01:07:52,110
Do you ever argue?

1802
01:07:52,620 --> 01:07:53,140
Hardly ever.

1803
01:07:53,510 --> 01:07:55,180
I doubt Michael would mind.

1804
01:07:56,070 --> 01:07:57,110
We baked a cake.

1805
01:07:57,550 --> 01:07:58,590
Baked a cake?

1806
01:07:59,220 --> 01:07:59,980
Dinner date.

1807
01:07:59,980 --> 01:08:01,270
Did you ever think about me?

1808
01:08:01,270 --> 01:08:02,900
You didn't answer me straight.

1809
01:08:02,900 --> 01:08:04,070
You're hesitating now.

1810
01:08:04,070 --> 01:08:05,110
Same as me.

1811
01:08:05,110 --> 01:08:06,110
His first impression.

1812
01:08:06,980 --> 01:08:07,700
You'll be with

1813
01:08:07,700 --> 01:08:08,660
whoever talks to you

1814
01:08:08,660 --> 01:08:09,620
or sticks to you.

1815
01:08:09,620 --> 01:08:11,070
I'm big on feedback.

1816
01:08:11,070 --> 01:08:12,180
Am I not?

1817
01:08:12,180 --> 01:08:13,700
Did I not give you any feedback?

1818
01:08:13,700 --> 01:08:15,270
You know whom you've been locked in.

1819
01:08:15,660 --> 01:08:16,060
No.

1820
01:08:16,060 --> 01:08:18,220
You're messing with my head.

1821
01:08:18,530 --> 01:08:19,650
Wait.

1822
01:08:20,220 --> 01:08:22,390
The heartfelt moment has begun.

1823
01:08:24,020 --> 01:08:25,020
Someone's leaving?

1824
01:08:25,950 --> 01:08:26,700
What?

1825
01:08:27,180 --> 01:08:28,100
How could it be him?

1826
01:08:28,100 --> 01:08:28,910
Why?

1827
01:08:29,270 --> 01:08:30,540
No way.

1828
01:08:30,540 --> 01:08:31,540
No one sees this coming.

1829
01:08:31,790 --> 01:08:32,430
I can't take it.

1830
01:08:32,660 --> 01:08:33,410
That's unexpected.

1831
01:08:34,180 --> 01:08:35,990
I don't want him to leave.

1832
01:08:38,390 --> 01:08:39,380
(Every Wed. at 12 pm)
I'll show you a magic trick.

1833
01:08:39,380 --> 01:08:40,100
(Pursue love on Balance Island)
Don't move.

1834
01:08:40,100 --> 01:08:40,780
(Curious)
Okay.

1835
01:08:40,790 --> 01:08:42,270
I know this one.

1836
01:08:42,390 --> 01:08:43,060
Is it this card?

1837
01:08:43,080 --> 01:08:43,750
Nope.

1838
01:08:43,750 --> 01:08:44,520
It's over.

1839
01:08:44,520 --> 01:08:45,270
That went wrong.

1840
01:08:45,480 --> 01:08:45,920
Hold on.

1841
01:08:49,560 --> 01:08:50,640
That's a bit better though.

1842
01:08:50,640 --> 01:08:51,470
Look at your tricks.

1843
01:08:51,920 --> 01:08:52,750
Do you want to

1844
01:08:52,750 --> 01:08:53,750
lock in with someone

1845
01:08:54,310 --> 01:08:55,640
or are you still hesitating?

1846
01:08:55,830 --> 01:08:56,350
Thanks.

1847
01:08:59,120 --> 01:09:01,000
Are you completely sure
about your choice?

1848
01:09:01,270 --> 01:09:01,610
How...

1849
01:09:01,610 --> 01:09:02,580
(Hesitant)
did you know?

1850
01:09:02,580 --> 01:09:03,380
(Bro, you get me)

1851
01:09:03,440 --> 01:09:05,230
Do you think
I've got you all figured out?

1852
01:09:05,750 --> 01:09:07,830
I can't hide it.

1853
01:09:08,300 --> 01:09:09,860
(Watch Live and Love with us
on Thurs. at 12 pm)

1854
01:09:09,870 --> 01:09:10,440
Here we go.

1855
01:09:10,440 --> 01:09:11,260
Choice.

1856
01:09:11,260 --> 01:09:11,960
(Please select)

1857
01:09:11,960 --> 01:09:13,830
Jiayi's energetic day kicks off again.

1858
01:09:13,830 --> 01:09:15,160
Like that cop questioning scene.

1859
01:09:15,160 --> 01:09:16,750
(Spies probing each other)
Are they spies?

1860
01:09:16,750 --> 01:09:17,920
This is way too hard.

1861
01:09:18,100 --> 01:09:19,460
(Stunned)

1862
01:09:20,670 --> 01:09:22,310
Bro, this one…

1863
01:09:22,310 --> 01:09:22,830
Just give...

1864
01:09:22,830 --> 01:09:23,670
(Secret)

1865
01:09:23,670 --> 01:09:24,830
Messed it up.

1866
01:09:24,830 --> 01:09:27,960
Huang Jiawei is seriously impressive.

1867
01:09:27,960 --> 01:09:29,790
The village chief is over the moon.

1868
01:09:29,790 --> 01:09:32,480
He's so thrilled
he's struggling to hide it.

1869
01:09:32,480 --> 01:09:35,270
He's about to break into a street dance
at the door.

1870
01:09:35,980 --> 01:09:36,980
(Better run first)

1871
01:09:37,120 --> 01:09:39,670
If it were me,
I'd write my name with my mouth.

1872
01:09:39,670 --> 01:09:42,670
No clue what choice
everyone will make next.
